data.description: If you're on the hunt for a cozy home with great features, then look no further than 354 Colorado St in Fairfield! This beautiful home offers 3 spacious bedrooms and a modern bathroom, perfect for relaxing and unwinding after a long day. With a remodeled kitchen, new flooring, and fresh paint, you won't find a better place to call home. Don't wait to see it in person. Schedule a showing today and experience the charm and comfort of this wonderful home for yourself!
